BC Post To View extension CONFIG

This document is a general configuration guide to the BC Post To View extension settings

BC Post To View Extension Settings
======================================

1. Default Extension Settings
   --------------------------

   Upon installing and activating the extension, one may need to alter these configuration settings.

   File: bcposttoview/settings/module.ini.append.php

   <?php /* #?ini charset="iso-8859-1"?

   [ModuleSettings]
   ExtensionRepositories[]=bcposttoview
   # Provided Modules
   ModuleList[]=posttoview
   ModuleList[]=defaultfilter
   ModuleList[]=customfilter01
   ModuleList[]=customfilter02
   # ModuleList[]=customfilter03
   # ModuleList[]=customfilter04

   */ ?>

   File: bcposttoview/settings/site.ini.append.php

   <?php /* #?ini charset="iso-8859-1"?

   [RoleSettings]
   PolicyOmitList[]=posttoview
   PolicyOmitList[]=defaultfilter
   PolicyOmitList[]=customfilter01
   PolicyOmitList[]=customfilter02

   */ ?>

2. Requirements
   ------------
      For more information on this subject please see doc/INSTALL

